---------------------------
0. Ahead of Time

In order to get ready for class you need to do a few things ahead of time:

- GOOGLE ACCOUNT If you don't already have a Google account you can [create one for free](https://accounts.google.com/signup)
- ANDROID STUDIO [Download and install Android Studio](http://developer.android.com/sdk/index.html)
- DEVICE PREP if you have an Android phone with Android Jellybean (4.1-4.3), KitKat (4.4), Lollipop (5.x), or Marshmallow (6.x) [Enable developer options](http://www.androidauthority.com/enable-developer-options-569223/) on your device to be able to connect with your computer
- GITHUB ACCOUNT If you don't already have a github account you can [create one for free](https://github.com/personal)

